        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Kali112-kilavi">itu viṉaivalapāṅkiṟ ṟalaiviyai āṟṟiṭaik kaṇṭu, viṉaivala-pāṅkiṟ ṟalaivaṉ vilakki nakaiyāṭi iruvaruñ cilamoḻi kūṟiyavaḻi avaḷ kūṭṭattiṟku uṭampaṭṭatu. itu kaikkiḷai.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en"/>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="Kali112">
                <l>yāriva ṉeṉṉai vilakkuvā ṉīruḷar </l>
                <l>pūntā maraippōtu tanta viravuttārk </l>
                <l>kallāp potuvaṉai nīmāṟu niṉṉoṭu </l>
                <l>collalōm peṉṟā remar; </l>
                <l rend="space">ellā, kaṭāaya kaṇṇāṟ kalaiiya nōyceyyu </l>
                <l>naṭāak karumpamaṉṟa tōḷāraik kāṇiṉ </l>
                <l>viṭāalōm peṉṟā remar; </l>
                <l rend="space">kaṭāayār, nallāraik kāṇiṉ vilakki nayantavar </l>
                <l>pallita ḻuṇkaṇṇun tōḷum pukaḻpāṭa </l>
                <l>nallatu kaṟpittār maṉṟa numar peritum </l>
                <l>valla remarkaṭ ceyal; </l>
                <l rend="space">ōo, vaḻaṅkāp poḻutunī kaṉṟumēyp pāypōl </l>
                <l>vaḻaṅka laṟivā ruraiyārē lemmai  </l>
                <l>yikaḻntārē yaṉṟō vemar;</l>
                <l rend="space">okkum, </l>
                <l>aṟivalyā ṉellā viṭu; </l>
                <l rend="space">viṭēṉyā, ṉeṉṉī kuṟitta tiruṅkūntā </l>
                <l>ṉiṉṉaiyeṉ muṉṉiṉṟu </l>
                <l>collalōm peṉṟamai yaṉṟi yavaṉainī </l>
                <l>pullalōm peṉṟa tuṭaiyarō mella </l>
                <l>muyaṅkuniṉ muḷḷeyi ṟuṇku mevaṉkolō </l>
                <l>māyap potuva ṉuraitta vuraiyellām </l>
                <l>vāyāva tāyiṟ ṟalaippaṭṭām poyyāyiṟ </l>
                <l>cāyaliṉ mārpiṟ kamaḻtār kuḻaittaniṉ </l>
                <l>ṉāyita ḻuṇkaṇ pacappat taṭameṉṟōḷ </l>
                <l>cāyiṉu mēe ruṭaittu.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
                <l>Who is this one who blocks me?</l>
                <l>You, unlearned herdsman with a mixed garland</l>
                <l>given by lotus buds with flowers that smooth the water,</l>
                <l corresp="1-4">our people have said to avoid speaking with you in reply. </l>
                <l>Hey,</l>
                <l>if you see girls with shoulders that are thickly grown with sugarcane that was not planted</l>
                <l rend="indent2">who cause [you] diffuse pain with [their] eyes that lure,</l>
                <l corresp="5-7">avoid letting [them] go, our people have said.</l>
                <l>Those who asked, to block [the way of] good girls when seeing them, coveting [them],</l>
                <l>[and] to sing the praise of their may-lashed kajal eyes and shoulders,</l>
                <l>something good they have taught [them], your people, and very</l>
                <l corresp="8-11">strong are the deeds from the side of our people.</l>
                <l>Oh, if those had not talked who know about [your] roaming</l>
                <l>as if you were grazing the calves at a time where one does not roam,</l>
                <l corresp="12-14">our people would have mocked us, isn’t it?</l>
                <l>Likely.</l>
                <l corresp="15-16">I know, hey, let go!</l>
                <l>I won’t let go – what is it that you intended,</l>
                <l corresp="16-17">standing in front of me, you with dark tresses?</l>
                <l>Apart from having said “avoid talking”, are there those </l>
                <l>who said “you avoid embracing him?” What of our </l>
                <l corresp="19-21">eating thorn teeth of you who gently embraces [me]?</l>
                <l corresp="22">If all the words spoken by the deceitful herdsman</l>
                <l corresp="23">are true, if the lie is with us who met [him],</l>
                <l>even though, while your choice-lashed kajal eyes fade, </l>
                <l>[your] broad soft shoulders are emaciated, on which </l>
                <l>was squashed the fragrant garland by [his] graceful, pleasing chest, </l>
                <l corresp="24-26">it possesses beauty.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
